<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Mir - Freelancer Acknowledgment & Portfolio</title>
  <style>
    /* Reset */
    body,
    html {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
      background-color: #faf9f7;
      color: #333333;
      line-height: 1.6;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 580px;
      margin: 48px auto;
      background: #fffefb;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 10px 48px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid #e2dcd3;
    }

    h1 {
      font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      color: #775DA6;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      text-align: center;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      margin: 20px 0;
      max-width: 100%;
      color: #333333;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #775DA6;
      /* background-color: #a87c52; */
      color: #fff9f2 !important;
      padding: 14px 42px;
      border-radius: 28px;
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-decoration: none;
      /* box-shadow: 0 5px 12px #5e4886; */
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: block;
      width: fit-content;
    }

    .cta-button:hover {
      background-color: #5e4886;
      box-shadow: 0 7px 16px #d3bbff;
    }

    .acknowledgment {
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      border-left: 5px solid #775DA6;
      padding: 26px 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #775DA6;
      max-width: 560px;
      margin: 40px auto 0 auto;
      line-height: 1.65;
      text-align: left;
      font-style: normal;
      /* box-shadow: inset 0 0 8px #d3bbff; */
    }

    .acknowledgment strong {
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #775DA6;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 48px;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #5f5f5f;
      text-align: center;
      font-style: italic;
      user-select: none;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .container {
        padding: 30px 24px;
      }

      .acknowledgment {
        font-size: 1rem;
        padding: 20px 24px;
      }
    }

    footer p {
      font-size: 14px;
      margin: 4px 0;
      color: #6b6b6b;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <section class="container" role="main" aria-label="Portfolio introduction and message acknowledgment email">
    <h1>Hi <%= name %>!</h1>
    <p>
      I’m <strong>Mihir Kasodariya</strong>, a MERN stack developer passionate about creating meaningful, scalable web
      applications
      with a personal touch.
    </p>

    <!-- Centered stats table -->
    <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"
      style="margin: 36px auto 52px auto; font-weight: 600; color: #333333; font-family: Georgia, serif; max-width: 300px; width: 100%; text-align: center;">
      <tr>
        <td style="border-left: none; padding: 0 24px;">
          <div style="font-size: 2.1rem; color: #333333; margin-bottom: 6px; text-align: center;">20+</div>
          Projects completed
        </td>
        <td style="border-left: 1px solid #d9cfc5; padding-left: 24px;">
          <div style="font-size: 2.1rem; color: #333333; margin-bottom: 6px; text-align: center;">5+</div>
          Clients worked with
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    <p>If you have an idea or project you’d like to discuss, I’d love to connect and collaborate!</p>

    <a href="<%= portfolio_domain %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="cta-button"
      aria-label="Explore Mir's portfolio">Explore My Portfolio</a>

    <aside class="acknowledgment" style="text-align:start" aria-live="polite" aria-atomic="true"
      aria-label="Acknowledgment message">
      <p style="text-align: start;">
        I have received your message and appreciate you reaching out.
      </p>
      <p style="text-align: start;">
        I will review your inquiry and get back to you within 24–48 hours.
      </p>
      <p style="text-align: start;">
        If your request is urgent, feel free to reply directly to this email.
      </p>
    </aside>

    <footer class="footer" aria-label="Footer information">
      <p><strong>© 2023</strong> Mihir Kasodariya – MERN Stack Developer</p>
      <p>Looking forward to working with you!</p>
    </footer>
  </section>
</body>

</html>